MICHAEL WANG 
LETTER OF COMMITMENT  
Your signature below indicates your intent to support the Mindboard, Inc. upon award to Mindboard, 
Inc. the Maryland Judiciary PeopleSoft Support Resources RFP# K25-0003-29 contract work.   
Your signature also provides your consent for the Mindboard team to submit your updated resume in 
support of its proposal, and that you have not and will not authorize any other entity to submit your 
resume in support of its work or proposal.  
By signing below, you also acknowledge that this letter of intent is not an offer of employment nor a 
contract for employment. You acknowledge that any offer from Mindboard would be contained in an 
offer letter, outlining the proposed terms and conditions of employment.  
You acknowledge the following statements: 1) I grant permission to Mindboard to use my resume, and 
2) I am willing to work for Mindboard on the instant solicitation.
